A function that returns a map of bundle names to their dependencies.


```typescript
export type BundleGraphAdder = (manifest: QwikManifest) => Record<string, {
    imports?: string[];
    dynamicImports?: string[];
}>;
```
**References:** [QwikManifest](#qwikmanifest)

